Manufacturing Protection Signature Utility

Description:
------------
This utility verifies the signature generated on a target board.
The signature is specific to each board, since each has its own
pair of private an public key. This utility verfies the signature
with the public key.

Build instructions:
-------------------
gcc -L/usr/lib -lssl -lcrypto -o verify main.c

Usage:
------
./verify -m 7A5D4dA3 \
         -k 040139C932F04525D083E15E3236DD1DCA625B2D0B14C13BA7FAA9C50C16619CE0F4C207AA609E4AAE586DF7FEE72F829F3B59CBF49F8F34C34ECA39EBD58E73CE \
         -c E85E34E4BF56CAA32DA858C0279C50A7E64E1136A23E51BF7C04CDA56389EE56 \
         -d 4A3C7A3725E1F7DDE41396393C88136B019633ED7BB33B689B78B25E06D42538

More information can be found on www.nxp.com - AN13222.
